lead_paragraph: Fox's live production of "Grease" fought rain, wind and personal tragedy to emerge a winner, with its audience of 12.2 million people eclipsing viewership for the last two musicals presented on NBC.

headline.main: 'Grease' Fights Through Rain, Tragedy to Reach 12.2 Million
